{"tid":2364873,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印尼總統公開接種中國科興武肺疫苗 九千萬共產黨黨員及習近平表示 ... ...","createTime":"2021-01-13T10:14:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T12:46:42.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"26925300c1d552b042a36e90edb6979936265c66","tid":2364873,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:14:43.000Z","msg":"印尼總統佐科維多多公開接種中國科興新冠疫苗<br />\n<br />\n印尼批准緊急使用中國科興生物研發的新型冠狀病毒疫苗後，總統佐科維多多成為首名接種者。<br />\n<br />\n佐科維多多先量度血壓，然後接受疫苗注射，過程由電視直播，以增強印尼民眾信心，當地醫學會主席亦接種了疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n印尼是中國以外第一個國家，對採用科興疫苗開綠燈，當地食品及藥物管理局說，後期臨床測試的臨時結果顯示，科興疫苗的有效率為65.3%。印尼當局計劃，為全國大約三分之二人口、即超過1億8千萬人接種疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570131-20210113.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570131-20210113.htm&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEUn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=99e3bf30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570131-20210113.htm&h=227b8261\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570131-20210113.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c16c73059adb0bdfe2d9b442093b04f1f71f6432","tid":2364873,"uid":83609,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:19:17.000Z","msg":"疫苗效率咁低打嚟做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97684da18156e77a802d0cc54e8809addcdf63b","tid":2364873,"uid":59868,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:19:58.000Z","msg":"印尼總統：打兩枝咪100%囉"},{"pid":"49ddf4f245c1075067c7a3c58d50636bd1fbf305","tid":2364873,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d97684da18156e77a802d0cc54e8809addcdf63b","tid":2364873,"uid":59868,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:19:58.000Z","msg":"印尼總統：打兩枝咪100%囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:23:25.000Z","msg":"諗起咩百步蛇嗰個笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\